  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class NonResponsiveConsumerEvent
extends KafkaEvent
    An event that is emitted when a consumer is not responding to the poll; a possible indication that the broker is down.
    从以下版本开始:
    1.3.1
